Revision history for Test-YAML-Valid

0.04	9 January 2010
        Add support for YAML::<Anything>, including ::Tiny and ::XS

0.03	31 January 2007
	Add Win32 support
	Fix tests (different messages with different Test::Builder versions)

0.02    30 January 2007
        Add support for YAML::Syck
	Add &yaml_files_ok()

0.01    29 January 2007
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

